  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F.",
    "Chop new potatoes into even pieces, toss with olive oil, salt, and pepper.",
    "Arrange on a baking sheet. Drizzle with butter and sprinkle dill and parsley over top.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Add minced garlic to the pan drippings in the oven, then stir in balsamic vinegar.",
    "Reduce sauce by half and pour over hot potatoes, tossing gently.",
    "Serve immediately."
